<EPIGRAPH>
<Q><BIBL><HI>JOB XXVII.6</HI></BIBL>
<P>My Righteou&s;ne&s;s I hold fa&s;t, and will not let it go: my Heart &s;hall not reproach me &s;o long as I live.</P></Q>
